trans-unit.source: Contains the data sent to a tracking service by the runtime tracking infrastructure when an <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint"></xref> is matched.
trans-unit.target: Innehåller data som skickas till en spårningstjänst av spårning körningsinfrastrukturen när en <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint"> </xref> matchas.

trans-unit.source: It is also used in the return list of the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance.ActivityEvents*> property.
trans-unit.target: Det används också i returnerar listan över de <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance.ActivityEvents*>egenskap.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance.ActivityEvents*>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] When the runtime tracking infrastructure matches an <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint> in a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>, it sends an ActivityTrackingRecord to the tracking service over the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel> associated with that tracking service.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]När spårning körningsinfrastrukturen matchar en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint>i en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>, skickar den ett ActivityTrackingRecord till Spårningstjänsten över den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel>som är associerade med den Spårningstjänsten.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint>

trans-unit.source: The tracking service can perform whatever action is needed on the data in the tracking record.
trans-unit.target: Spårningstjänsten kan utföra åtgärder som krävs på data i spårningsposten.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: This constructor is called by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Den här konstruktorn anropas av körningen spårning infrastruktur.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord"></xref> class by using the specified parameters.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord"> </xref> klassen med hjälp av de angivna parametrarna.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Type> of the activity associated with the activity status event.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Type>för aktiviteten som är associerade med status aktivitetshändelse.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.QualifiedName%2A?displayProperty=fullName> of the activity associated with the activity status event.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.QualifiedName%2A?displayProperty=fullName> för aktiviteten som är associerade med status aktivitetshändelse.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Guid> that identifies the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext"></xref> of the activity associated with the activity status event.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Guid>som identifierar den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext"> </xref> för aktiviteten som är associerade med status aktivitetshändelse.</xref:System.Guid>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Guid> that identifies the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext"></xref> of the parent activity of the activity associated with the activity status event.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Guid>som identifierar den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext"> </xref> för den överordnade aktiviteten för aktiviteten som är associerade med status aktivitetshändelse.</xref:System.Guid>

trans-unit.source: One of the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus"></xref> values.
trans-unit.target: En av de <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus"> </xref> värden.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.DateTime> that indicates the date and time of the activity status event associated with the tracking record.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.DateTime>som anger datum och tid för händelsen aktivitetens status som associeras med spårningsposten.</xref:System.DateTime>

trans-unit.source: The relative order in which the activity status event associated with this tracking record occurred in the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Den relativa ordning i vilken status aktivitetshändelse som är associerade med den här spårningsposten uppstod i arbetsflödesinstansen.

trans-unit.source: A null reference (<xref uid="langword_csharp_Nothing" name="Nothing" href=""></xref> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: En null-referens (<xref uid="langword_csharp_Nothing" name="Nothing" href=""> </xref> i Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: This field is not set for an <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Det här fältet har inte angetts för en <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the common language runtime (CLR) type of the activity associated with this <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger den gemensamma language runtime (CLR) typen för aktiviteten som associeras med den här <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: ActivityType is set by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: ActivityType anges av körningsmiljön spårning infrastruktur.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Type> of the activity for which this <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord"></xref> was created.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Type>för aktiviteten som den här <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord"> </xref> har skapats.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of annotations associated with the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint"></xref> that was matched.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar mängden anteckningar som är associerade med den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint"> </xref> som matchades.

trans-unit.source: This property is set by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Den här egenskapen anges av körningen spårning infrastruktur.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingAnnotationCollection"></xref> that contains the annotations that are associated with the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint"></xref> that corresponds to this tracking record.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingAnnotationCollection"> </xref> som innehåller anteckningar som är associerade med den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint"> </xref> som motsvarar av spårningsposten.

trans-unit.source: Gets a list that contains any data extracted from the workflow for the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint"></xref> that was matched.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar en lista som innehåller alla data som hämtats från arbetsflödet för den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint"> </xref> som matchades.

trans-unit.source: When an <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint> is matched, the runtime tracking infrastructure can extract data from the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: När en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint>matchas, runtime spårning infrastruktur kan extrahera data från arbetsflödesinstansen.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint>

trans-unit.source: The data to be extracted is specified by <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.Extracts%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Data som ska extraheras har angetts av <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.Extracts%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.Extracts%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.Extracts%2A?displayProperty=fullName> can contain two kinds of objects: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract> objects specify member data to be extracted from the activity associated with the activity status event; and, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> objects specify member data to be extracted from the root activity of the workflow.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.Extracts%2A?displayProperty=fullName>kan innehålla två typer av objekt: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract>objekt ange medlemsdata extraheras från den aktivitet som är associerade med status aktivitetshändelse; och <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract>objekt ange medlemsdata extraheras från rotaktiviteten av arbetsflödet.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract></xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.Extracts%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Both of these extract types can also specify annotations to be returned with the extracted data.
trans-unit.target: Dessa båda Extraheringsjobb typer kan också ange anteckningar som ska returneras med data som extraheras.

trans-unit.source: The runtime tracking infrastructure encapsulates each piece of extracted data and its associated annotations in a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem>, and adds this <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem> to Body.
trans-unit.target: Spårning körningsinfrastrukturen kapslar in varje typ av data som hämtas och dess associerade anteckningar i en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem>, och lägger till detta <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem>till brödtexten.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem>

trans-unit.source: This property is set by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Den här egenskapen anges av körningen spårning infrastruktur.

trans-unit.source: A list of <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem"></xref> objects each of which contains a single piece of extracted data and its associated annotations.
trans-unit.target: En lista över <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem"> </xref> objekt som innehåller en enda typ av data som hämtas och dess associerade anteckningar.

trans-unit.source: Context of the activity.
trans-unit.target: Kontexten för aktiviteten.

trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Guid>som identifierar den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext"> </xref> för aktiviteten som är associerade med status aktivitetshändelse.</xref:System.Guid>

trans-unit.target: Always <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> for an <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord"></xref>.

trans-unit.source: This property is set by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Den här egenskapen anges av körningen spårning infrastruktur.

trans-unit.target: Händelseargument kan har ingen betydelse för en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord>och är alltid en null-referens (`Nothing`).</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord>

trans-unit.source: This property is set by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Den här egenskapen anges av körningen spårning infrastruktur.

trans-unit.target: En null-referens (<xref uid="langword_csharp_Nothing" name="Nothing" href=""></xref>) för en <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the date and time that the activity status event occurred.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger datum och tid då aktiviteten status händelsen inträffade.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.DateTime> is Greenwich Mean Time (UTC).
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.DateTime>är Greenwich Mean Time (UTC).</xref:System.DateTime>

trans-unit.source: EventDateTime is set by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: EventDateTime anges av körningsmiljön spårning infrastruktur.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.DateTime> value.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.DateTime>värde.</xref:System.DateTime>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that indicates the order in the workflow instance of the activity status event that matched the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger ett värde som anger ordningen i arbetsflödesinstansen i händelsen aktivitetens status som matchade den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: EventOrder indicates the relative order of the event that matched the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint> within the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: EventOrder anger den relativa ordningen för händelsen som matchade den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint>i arbetsflödesinstansen.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint>

trans-unit.source: EventOrder is unique within a workflow instance, but it is not guaranteed to be sequential.
trans-unit.target: EventOrder är unika inom en arbetsflödesinstans, men det är inte säkert att vara sekventiella.

trans-unit.source: EventOrder is set by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: EventOrder anges av körningsmiljön spårning infrastruktur.

trans-unit.source: A value that indicates the order of the activity status event in the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Ett värde som anger status aktivitetshändelse i arbetsflödesinstansen ordning.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the execution status of the activity associated with this <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger körningsstatusen för aktiviteten som associeras med den här <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: A workflow instance only emits activity status events when the execution status of an activity instance changes.
trans-unit.target: En arbetsflödesinstans avger endast aktiviteten statushändelser när status för körning av en Aktivitetsinstans ändras.

trans-unit.source: Therefore an <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint> can only be matched when an activity execution status change occurs.
trans-unit.target: Därför en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint>kan bara kopplas när en aktivitet körning status ändras.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint>

trans-unit.source: ExecutionStatus contains the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus?displayProperty=fullName> that triggered the match and caused the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord> to be sent.
trans-unit.target: ExecutionStatus innehåller den <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus?displayProperty=fullName>som utlöste matchningen och gjorde den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord>skickas.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: It reflects the current status of the activity instance.
trans-unit.target: Den visar den aktuella statusen för Aktivitetsinstansen.

trans-unit.source: ExecutionStatus is set by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: ExecutionStatus anges av körningsmiljön spårning infrastruktur.

trans-unit.source: One of the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus"></xref> values.
trans-unit.target: En av de <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus"> </xref> värden.

trans-unit.source: Context of the parent activity.
trans-unit.target: Kontexten för den överordnade aktiviteten.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Guid> that identifies the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext"></xref> of the activity associated with the activity status event.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Guid>som identifierar den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext"> </xref> för aktiviteten som är associerade med status aktivitetshändelse.</xref:System.Guid>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the identifier of the activity associated with this <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger identifieraren för aktiviteten som associeras med den här <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: QualifiedName is set by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: QualifiedName anges av körningsmiljön spårning infrastruktur.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.QualifiedName%2A?displayProperty=fullName> of the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"></xref> for which this tracking record was created.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.QualifiedName%2A?displayProperty=fullName> av den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"> </xref> för av spårningsposten har skapats.
